<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 22 at 8:45AM MST  by NWS Pueblo</headline>
<description>...Light to moderate snow continues this morning...
Light to moderate snow is expected to continue along the I-25
corridor and Highway 50. Although snowfall amounts remain light,
brief periods of reduced visibility will be possible, which could
lead to hazardous travel conditions. Conditions are expected to
improve through late morning.
For those traveling in this area, please use caution.</description>
